#

Chickpea Salad with Feta and Cucumber

10 min
$8.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mediterranean

Course:

Main or Side Dish

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuickNo-Cook

Description

A refreshing and healthy salad bursting with flavors and textures, perfect for a quick meal or a side dish!

Ingredients

  • canned chickpeas: 1 can (15 oz)
  • cucumber: 1 medium, diced
  • feta cheese: 1 cup, crumbled
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup, halved
  • red onion: 1/4, finely chopped
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped (optional)
